OL,3,CFactory that employs dozens of
OL,4,Cdisabled adults facing closure
OL,6,FA Hampshire charity that employs
OL,7,Fdozens of disabled people says it's
OL,8,Ffighting for survival due to delayed
OL,9,Fpayments from the Government's Access
OL,10,Fto Work Plus scheme.
OL,12,FYateley Industries claims it's around
OL,13,F#150,000 out of pocket, which has been
OL,14,Fowed to them since October last year.
OL,16,FThe charity was set up in 1937 to give
OL,17,Fpeople with disabilities as much
OL,18,Findependence as possible.
