OL,3,CFactory that employs dozens of
OL,4,Cdisabled adults facing closure
OL,6,FIt currently employs 58 people at its
OL,7,Fsupported factory which offers light
OL,8,Fassembly hand packing and shrink
OL,9,Fwrapping.
OL,11,FThe factory relies on funding to cover
OL,12,Fthe cost of things like specialist
OL,13,Fequipment and support staff.
OL,15,FYateley Industries CEO, Sheldon
OL,16,FMcMullan, said: "We've tried all sorts
OL,17,Fof diplomatic interventions to try and
OL,18,Fget them to pay us but it's like
OL,19,Fshouting into the darkness, they just
OL,20,Fdon't respond."
