OL,6,F"They come back with arbitrary
OL,7,Frejections of claims that we've made
OL,8,Fand the paperwork has increased four-
OL,9,Ffold."
OL,11,F"At the end of this month (March
OL,12,F2025), it will be #186,000 that we're
OL,13,Fowed.
OL,15,F"If we don't get that money, we might
OL,16,Fhave to consider closing the factory,
OL,17,Fso 58 disabled people could
OL,18,Fpotentially be out of work."
