OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,FWork and Pensions said: "Helping
OL,8,Fpeople into good work and financial
OL,9,Findependence is at the heart of our
OL,10,FPlan for Change, but the broken social
OL,11,Fsecurity system we inherited is
OL,12,Ffailing people who can and have the
OL,13,Fpotential to work, as well as the
OL,14,Fpeople it's meant to be there for.
OL,16,F"As part of our reforms, we are
OL,17,Fconsulting on the future of Access to
OL,18,FWork, and encourage people to have
OL,19,Ftheir views and voices heard on how
OL,20,Fthey think the programme could be
OL,21,Fimproved."
